  <p>
    Fula Devi Memorial Sewa Sansthan is a charitable institution registered in
    Bihar, India, in 2022.
  </p>
  <p>
    It is small by intention. It supports the education of one child and makes a
    charitable contribution each year. It has helped eligible families below the
    poverty line access the Ayushman Bharat health insurance scheme.
  </p>
  <p>The institution grows through work, not expansion.</p>
